---
/** FeatureCards — Figma node 8:333 */
---

<section class="bg-light-gray py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-[1232px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section label + divider -->
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-text mb-4">Why it matters</p>
    <div class="w-full h-px bg-accent mb-12 sm:mb-16"></div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h2 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[56px] lg:leading-[1.25] tracking-tight mb-16 sm:mb-20 max-w-3xl">
      What changes when someone's actually on your side
    </h2>

    <!-- Feature cards grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-12 gap-y-16">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3">You stop overpaying</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text leading-relaxed">Most businesses I review are paying 20-40% too much on card processing. I find where the money's going and get it back.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3">Your till and card machine work together</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text leading-relaxed">No more end-of-day discrepancies. Integrated systems that talk to each other, set up properly from day one.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Spacer for offset layout on desktop -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block"></div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3">I pick up the phone</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text leading-relaxed">Your card machine dies mid-service? You call me. I answer, and we fix it.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3">No vendor lock-in</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text leading-relaxed">I work with 8+ providers. I recommend what fits your business, not what pays me the highest commission.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
